;;;                             꼬치구이가 어렵지도 않고 재료도 다양하고~ 또, 요건 치즈라서 와인이나 맥주안주로도 좋더라구요.   연말에 펜션이나 캠핑가서 바베큐 파티할때~ 꼬치 몇개 준비해서 같이 구우면 딱~ 좋을 거 같아요 ㅎㅎ^^                         [이 포스팅은 동원 F&B에서 무료지원된 '구워먹는치즈'제품을 이용하여 작성한 글입니다.]      ","images":["http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141110_275/chungsun1_1415585291006iplan_JPEG/IMG_0683.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141110_266/chungsun1_14155852876633jX6f_JPEG/IMG_0600.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141110_284/chungsun1_1415585287913O5I5e_JPEG/IMG_0603.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141110_228/chungsun1_1415585288103QS1BH_JPEG/IMG_0604.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141110_220/chungsun1_14155852882341R11r_JPEG/IMG_0605.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141110_156/chungsun1_1415585288438mmazg_JPEG/IMG_0606.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141110_225/chungsun1_141558528855353ytu_JPEG/IMG_0608.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141110_8/chungsun1_141558528868376NEK_JPEG/IMG_0609.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141110_134/chungsun1_14155852888703e92z_JPEG/IMG_0610.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141110_119/chungsun1_1415585289032kO1bl_JPEG/IMG_0612.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141110_105/chungsun1_1415585289149Td6Es_JPEG/IMG_0613.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141110_145/chungsun1_1415585289347AoiJS_JPEG/IMG_0616.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141110_66/chungsun1_1415585289532BWdWC_JPEG/IMG_0673.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141110_4/chungsun1_1415585289751f2uen_JPEG/IMG_0675.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141110_288/chungsun1_1415585290680GdfCe_JPEG/IMG_0682.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141110_275/chungsun1_1415585291006iplan_JPEG/IMG_0683.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141110_43/chungsun1_14155852912801bf5F_JPEG/IMG_0687.JPG?type=","http://mblogthu